<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bottom-adj">bottom <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bɒtəm/    美 /'bɑːtəm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>底下的；底部的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the bottom line 
底线</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Put your clothes in the <strong>bottom drawer</strong>. 
把你的衣服放在最下面的抽屉里。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>最末的；最差的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was <strong>bottom of the class</strong> in Spanish. 
我的西班牙语在班上是最差的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>came bottom</strong> with 12 points. 
我们以12分垫底。</p></div></div>